      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "## Trans-Hub Localizer 0.1.2\n\nTrans-Hub Localizer is now available as a public release for Obsidian desktop users. It localizes supported community-plugin names, descriptions, settings, commands, and interface text into your selected language, while leaving your vault notes and third-party plugin files unchanged.\n\n语枢 · 插件本地化现已面向 Obsidian 桌面端用户公开发布。它可将已支持的社区插件名称、说明、设置、命令和界面文本本地化为你选择的语言，同时保持库笔记和第三方插件文件不被修改。\n\n### Install / 安装\n\nDownload `main.js`, `manifest.json`, and `styles.css`, then place all three files in:\n\n```text\n<vault-config-dir>/plugins/trans-hub-plugin-localizer/\n```\n\n下载 `main.js`、`manifest.json`、`styles.css`，并将三者放入以上目录；随后在 Obsidian 中启用插件。\n\n### Safety and privacy / 安全与隐私\n\n- Localization is applied at runtime; plugin files and vault notes stay unchanged.\n- 本地化在运行时应用；插件文件和库笔记保持不变。\n- The client has no advertising or client-side telemetry.\n- 客户端不包含广告或客户端遥测。\n\nFor the complete usage, privacy, and build details, see the [bilingual README](https://github.com/SakenW/trans-hub-obsidian-localizer/blob/main/README.md).\n\n完整的使用、隐私与构建说明请参阅[双语 README](https://github.com/SakenW/trans-hub-obsidian-localizer/blob/main/README.md)。",
